It‚Äôs A Family Affair At Mia‚Äôs Italian Kitchen
From Nonna‚Äôs kitchen to your table, enjoy authentic Italian cuisine at Mia‚Äôs Italian Kitchen. Our robust menu evokes nostalgia with made-from-scratch family recipes designed for sharing. Craveable comforts include Mia‚Äôs Family-Style Dining, classic starters, salads and sandwiches, housemade pasta, 800-degree brick oven pan pizzas, and more. Join us daily for lunch and dinner, during the weekdays for our extended happy hour, and on weekends for bottomless brunch.
In the heart of all the action, Mia‚Äôs Italian Kitchen is located just minutes from Disney Springs. Buon appetito!

Craveable Comforts
From family-style dining to housemade pasta and brick oven pizzas, Mia‚Äôs Italian Kitchen brings authentic Italian classics to your table. Explore our menus below and plan your next delicious visit!
Who Doesn‚Äôt Love Bottomless Brunch?
Join us every Saturday and Sunday for our bottomless brunch from 11 am to 3 pm. For $34.25*, select as many items from our brunch menu as you can mangia for an endlessly delicious weekend! Add bottomless Mimosas, Sparklers and Bloody Marys for just $24* more, because sometimes you need to toast more than once.
*Price is per person, all guests must choose this option.
Cheers to Happy Hour-ing A Little Longer
Enjoy our weekday happy hour from 12 to 7 pm
at the bar, pizza bar and sofa lounge. Nonna‚Äôs Tomato Gravy, Brick Oven Pan Pizza, Pepperoni Cheese Fries and Chicken Parmigiano Sliders are all available for just $5. Also enjoy two-for-one specials on our best-selling signature sangrias, wines, beers, and Italian-inspired cocktails. Saluti!
It‚Äôs a Family Affair
Great meals are made for sharing. Invite your friends, family, and loved ones to enjoy our family-style dining option. Choose any five items from our dinner menu, along with a salad and dessert selection, for just $39 per person*.
*Minimum of 2 guests¬†required.

La Dolce Vita | Celebrate Life‚Äôs Sweetest Moments
Step into Mia‚Äôs Italian Kitchen, where heritage and flavors seamlessly blend in every plate. Indulge in the artistry of house-made pastas, salads and Italian sandwiches that serve as a culinary passport to the streets of Italy. Mia‚Äôs invites guests to be part of a narrative etched in homemade pasta and the warmth of family.
Our spacious dining rooms can be transformed to create the perfect setting for all of your private event needs. Whether you are looking to host a large party or celebrate with a group of friends, we offer an experience they‚Äôll never forget. With accommodations of up to 450 guests, we have flexible seating and format options for private events, with full-service event coordination by our experienced staff members.

Christini‚Äôs Ristorante Italiano is the most awarded Italian fine dining restaurant in Orlando and the United States.
Our recipes are a classical interpretation of northern Italian cuisine. Dishes are prepared using only the freshest and highest quality ingredients. You will be impressed with the presentation of your meal, as our experienced staff presents each dish with astonishing attention to detail.
Christini‚Äôs has remained true to the award-winning dishes and recipes that have been served since day one. Order any dish and it will be prepared the same way it was prepared over two decades ago when the restaurant opened. Indulge your taste buds and prepare to be amazed by Orlando‚Äôs best Italian restaurant: Christini‚Äôs Ristorante Italiano.

About the Business
Manzzo Cuisine is a refined Italian restaurant with contemporary cuisine, located in the sophisticated area of Windermere, Orlando. While it is an elegant and exquisite space, where every detail has been carefully crafted to cater to the most discerning palates, Manzzo manages to combine this sophistication with accessible prices, making it a top gastronomic destination for those who appreciate good food and a welcoming environment.

With a diverse menu ranging from traditional appetizers like the Mixed Antipasto Manzzo to exquisite main courses like the Lobster with Sicilian Risotto, Manzzo stands out for the quality of its ingredients and the mastery in the preparation of each dish. Pasta options, such as the authentic Spaghetti alla Carbonara, and risottos, like the Pear and Gorgonzola Risotto, offer a true invitation to embark on a journey through the flavors of Italy.

To complete the experience, Manzzo Cuisine takes pride in its impressive wine cellar, housing a vast selection of the finest wines from different regions of the world. Each label has been carefully selected to perfectly complement the dishes on the menu, further elevating the dining experience and creating unforgettable moments for its visitors. Manzzo's commitment to providing a complete and memorable experience is reflected in the attention given to every detail, from the plate to the glass.

Celebrating Good Food, Good Company, and Good Times
At Nonno's Italian Restaurant, we believe that dining should be a celebration of good food, good company, and good times. That's why we strive to create an atmosphere that is warm, inviting, and imbued with the sights, sounds, and flavors of Italy. From the moment you step through our doors, you'll feel as if you have been transported to the bustling streets of New York or Rome, surrounded by the rich scents of freshly-baked bread, sauces bubbling on the stove, and a variety of traditional Italian dishes.
Classic New York-style Italian Cuisine
Our menu features classic New York-style Italian dishes made with only the freshest ingredients. Whether you're in the mood for a hearty pasta dish, a crispy flatbread, or a succulent entr√©e, we have something for everyone. And because we believe that good food is only half the story, our knowledgeable servers are always on hand to recommend dishes, answer questions, and make sure your dining experience is unforgettable.

Layla's Cavatappi Family Pasta Meal
Feed a family of 6 (or four teenagers!): 1 LARGE pan of your choice of salad (Italian, Garden, or Caesar), 2 Focaccia loaves of bread, 1 LARGE pan of Cavatappi Pasta slathered in our homemade Vodka Sauce ‚Äì heavy cream, vodka, Prosciutto di Parma, garlic, butter, Pecorino Romano, oregano, salt, and pepper ‚Äì and loaded up with our 100% All Natural & Gluten-Free Meatballs. FALL MENU IS HERE!

THE WING PACK IS BACK!
(Available for pre-order: TAKE OUT ONLY)
Order ahead for Game Day! We are baking, tossing, and serving up a 48 wing party platter for $94
PLACE YOUR ORDERS FOR GAME DAY PICKUP ‚Äî set your pickup time for Saturday ‚Äì Monday & we will text you when it‚Äôs ready!

By pre-ordering your wings for game day, you help our staff tremendously. It guarantees your order and helps our kitchens run more efficiently. Help us, help you.
order now
Don‚Äôt Bring Home Our Pizza Unless You‚Äôve Got the Stones to Do it Right
Because our dough has ZERO artificial ingredients, our pizza must be eaten right out of our oven for true authentic flavor. If you plan on bringing one home, we strongly suggest (like really, really strongly) you purchase one of our pizza stones. They‚Äôre only $20 and last forever. And, it‚Äôs the best way to recreate that same V Pizza flavor at home.
Here‚Äôs how:
Place the stone in your oven and crank it as high as it goes.
Put your pizza on the HOT stone for 60 seconds.
And boom! You‚Äôre back in Naples eating pizza the way it was intended.
Molto Bene!

The menu pays homage to the essence of the great Italian-American restaurants in New York City. Where delicious, exceptionally well-prepared food is served in settings that are simultaneously elegant, comfortable and unpretentious. Familiar dishes like Classic Chicken Parmesan, Bucatini Bolognese, and Spicy Vodka Rigate are elevated to a new level.

AUTHENTIC ITALIAN FOOD FOR DINE IN OR TO GO
At Brio, we believe that to eat well is to live well. We only use the freshest and highest quality ingredients, making sure that every meal is a truly memorable dining experience. Ask your server for the perfect wine or crafted cocktail to compliment our signature Carpaccio with shaved tender beef, capers, and mustard aioli to start your meal. Enjoy an authentic taste of Tuscany with our Spaghetti Bolognese or Pasta Brio. Tuscan inspired Italian restaurant menu is sure to satisfy. Make it a Brio dinner to remember with our double-cut New Zealand Lamb Chops, Grilled Chicken Marsala, or Gorgonzola Crusted Beef Medallions. Whether you‚Äôre enjoying a romantic dinner for two or celebrating a special occasion with family and friends, the Brio dinner menu is the perfect way to indulge in all your favorite Italian dishes.
We‚Äôre open seven days a week, offering lunch & dinner with Brunch on weekends. Reserve your table and
DINE IN
or
ORDER TO GO
for Brio Italian food delivery or curbside pickup. Planning a gathering for 20 or more? Click
GROUP DINING
to get all the details you need to plan your special event, birthday party, family celebration, or corporate event. Want the party delivered? Visit our
CATERING
page for easy ordering for 10 or more. Join us for a great Italian dinner in the restaurant or take out to enjoy at home.
Buon Appetito!

Business owner information
Jason C.
Business Owner
The Osprey promises a modern coastal cuisine menu designed to highlight the bounty of Florida's sustainable seafood.  The bar boasts a sophisticated beverage program and extensive wine list to complement the menu, evoking a sense of nostalgia and adventure with its classic cocktail interpretations. And the Oyster Bar, not to be missed, offers the best of Florida's local shellfish at an intimate Chef's Counter.

About the Business
Orlando's best selection of food trucks and craft beer!

We have eight vendors serving smash burgers, Spanish tapas and paella, pizza, cheesesteaks and sandwiches, tacos and nachos, sushi, coffee, and ice cream! With eight different cuisine styles to choose from, you're sure to find something for everyone in your group.

An open-air pavilion provides guests with covered indoor seating and an outdoor courtyard allows you to dine among the carts and under the stars. The bar features a rotating lineup of beers, ciders, and seltzers as well as an extensive can menu of craft beer, wine, and nonalcoholic beverages.

Culinary Masterpieces
Experience a culinary revival at The Boheme‚Äîwhere French Revival-inspired elegance meets inventive flavors. Discover a delectable and imaginative convergence of past and present, as locally sourced, heirloom ingredients are transformed into artfully plated masterpieces. Indulge in refined dining within a grand yet welcoming setting at Orlando's most iconic restaurant.

Menu
Our thoughtfully curated menu brings together tradition and creativity, transforming fresh, locally sourced ingredients into dishes that pay homage to the past and look forward to the future.
View Menus
A Canvas of Sophistication
As you cross the threshold, the soft glow of ambient lighting illuminates geometric forms and ornate details of stylish architecture.The atmosphere blends authenticity with refined beauty, setting the stage for an unforgettable dining experience. With live jazz in the air, the space is ideal for intimate dinners, lively celebrations, or our vibrant Sunday Jazz Brunches. Enjoy a signature European cocktail before your first course or savor premium spirits at the bar in a setting that combines sophistication with warmth.
Dine with a Muse
European dining is elevated with a fusion of innovation, artistry, and intuitive service. The Boheme‚Äôs menu elegantly reinterprets classic dishes via modern techniques applied to hand-selected ingredients. Our patrons indulge in an exceptional wine list, elegant cocktails, and imported beers to complement distinctively plated meals. Inspired by the French Revival, our culinary philosophy marries heritage with creativity, offering an experience where timeless flavors meet bold, modern expression.

Great Sunday Brunch
A great way to celebrate a Sunday! Nice Jazz with the singer in the background, a very good buffet, and excellent service. We feasted on their snow crabs brought steaming to the table and their fresh oysters. Our server ensured that we never ran low on food or our bottomless mimosas!
Kalu W./TripAdvisor
The Best
I came for Brunch, and it was absolutely phenomenal. They had live music with an extensive selection of food. To top it off, they had unlimited oysters and crab legs with bottomless mimosas. Definitely worth the price.
Shannon T./Yelp

Beverage Menu
Barrel Aged Cocktails
Smuggler's Courage
Patience is a virtue. We start with a brown butter washed blend of Brugal 1888 & Woodford Reserve bourbon. After that, we leave it to mature in charred virgin American oak barrels for 4-6 weeks. When it has reached the pinnacle of it's development, we add our house made spice rack demerara syrup for a transcendent cocktail experience. Infused with orange aroma and presented tableside.
36.
Bespoke Gentleman
Not for the faint of heart, our take on the classic boulevardier reaches new heights. Our blend of Michter's rye, Campari, and Carpano Antica become infused with coca nibs and barrel aged for 4-6 weeks in a charred virgin american oak barrel. Presented with fire tableside, with a high proof orange infusion.

Wine Flights
A flight of wines is so much more than just a tasting; it is actually a flavorful journey to Italy that lets you experience what the old country has to offer
Under a Tuscan Sun
Take a trip to Italy's best-known region, the land of castles and coastlines where the wine is always flowing freely. A classic fruit-driven Chianti is followed by the beautiful berry flavours from a Tuscan Sangiovese/Cabernet combination; Finished with a rich and powerful red blend. | 26
Crisp Italian Whites
These three crisp, soft and highly acidic Italian whites range from north to south, and are perfect to accompany almost any food dish without overpowering it. | 22
From the Hills of Piemonte
Piemonte is the land of rolling hills and fog which is famous for the world's most food-friendly wines. The perfect aperitif white wine is followed by a juicy Dolcetto and a dark rustic Nebbiolo. | 26
Limoncello Flight
A taste of three Fabrizia liqueurs, Sicilian Limoncello, Fabrizia di Crema and Fabrizia di Pistachio | 24

The Venetian Chop House Menus
Inspired Innovation
Executive Chef David Hackett brings an artful sophistication to every dish at The Venetian Chop House, sourcing the finest seasonal ingredients from the country‚Äôs top farms, ranches, and producers. Innovative Italian and steakhouse classics are presented with signature elegance alongside a playful dessert menu, signature craft cocktails, and an extensive, globally influenced wine list for an unforgettable‚Äîand effortless‚Äîfine dining experience.

Meet the Team
Chef Luis Taborda
Chef Luis Taborda
Luis moved from Colombia to Boston in 1986 and quickly rose through the ranks‚Äîstarting as a dishwasher and becoming a chef within two years. After serving as Sous Chef at Morton‚Äôs of Chicago, he brought his steakhouse expertise to Orlando, joining The Venetian Chop House as Chef du Cuisine in 2014.
Chef David Hackett
Chef David Hackett
Born and raised on Chicago‚Äôs South Side, David found his culinary calling at 12 and built his career across kitchens from Dubai to Savannah. A Washburne Culinary Institute grad and member of Chaine des Rotisseurs, he champions the use of fresh, wholesome ingredients,
and regularly takes part in local charity events.
Chef Jessica Bingham
Chef Jessica Bingham
With nearly 25 years in pastry arts, Jessica is known for showstopping creations like her Flaming Chocolate Sphere. When she‚Äôs not in the kitchen or mentoring young chefs, she‚Äôs immersed in her favorite sci-fi worlds‚ÄîStar Wars, Lord of the Rings, and Outlander.
Scott Lagrimanta
Scott Lagrimanta
Originally from Colorado, Scott traveled the world with the U.S. Air Force before settling in Orlando. He honed his skills at top restaurants including The Boathouse at Disney Springs and Quartino in Chicago. On his days off, you‚Äôll find him on the golf course or reminiscing about his BMX racing days‚Äîhe was once ranked among the country‚Äôs Top 50 competitors.
Highlights
Lobster Bisque
Velvety and rich, the Lobster Bisque offers a hint of sherry and is crowned with a golden, airy puff pastry dome.
Highlights
Ora King Salmon
Artfully prepared and presented, sustainably sourced Ora King Salmon is finished with a rich lemon beurre blanc.
Highlights
Lazy Italian Cocktail
An ode to effortless indulgence, this signature cocktail blends crisp vodka with citrus-forward limoncello for a refreshing finish.

Where can I add a missing visit for Dine Rewards?
Expand or collapse answer
Please visit
https://www.dine-rewards.com/
and click "Add a Visit." Enter the phone number associated with your Dine Rewards account and complete the form to have your credit manually applied. If you no longer have the receipt, please contact the restaurant directly and they will be happy to help you locate it.
Do you have outdoor seating?
Expand or collapse answer
Many of our restaurants have patio seating. Please contact your local Carrabba's to see if outdoor dining is available.
Do you have a Kids menu?
Expand or collapse answer
Yes, we do have a menu for kids 10 and under.

About Carrabba's Italian Grill
Orlando, FL
Offering authentic Italian cuisine passed down from our founders' family recipes, Carrabba's Italian Grill¬Æ uses only the best ingredients to prepare fresh and handmade dishes cooked to order in a lively exhibition kitchen. Featuring a wood-burning grill inspired by the many tastes of Italy, guests can enjoy signature dishes, including Chicken Bryan, Pollo Rosa Maria, Wood-Fire Grilled Steak and chops and classic Italian Pasta dishes in a welcoming, contemporary atmosphere.
Managing Partner: Toon Phan
Location: Corner of International Dr. and Icon Park next to Outback Steak House

Bella's Pizzeria & Italian Restaurant
Discover a new favorite by trying the top pizzas in Casselberry.

Local residents have made Bella's Pizzeria & Italian Restaurant one of the most popular in the area. Sample what they have to offer and see if you agree.

Many pizzerias in Casselberry offer more than just pizza, so try some other local top dishes. Pasta, salads, calzones, sandwiches, and more can all give you something different to enjoy. See why the locals rave about Bella's Supreme Pizza at Bella's Pizzeria & Italian Restaurant. This local favorite is popular for a reason.

Complete your meal with mozzarella sticks, it's a great way to make dinner into a feast.

A Slice partner for 7 years, this restaurant is a mainstay of the community. Try them for yourself and see why they're such a local favorite. You can get your pizza to go with curbside pickup from Bella's Pizzeria & Italian Restaurant. Grab something tasty on your way home. Check out some of the regular deals offered at Bella's Pizzeria & Italian Restaurant. The only thing better than pizza is pizza at a discount.

Pay by credit card to make the checkout process easier.

Check out social media for news and deals.

Escas Pizza
Discover a new favorite by trying the top pizzas in Lake Mary.

Local residents have made Escas Pizza one of the most popular in the area. Sample what they have to offer and see if you agree.

Many pizzerias in Lake Mary offer more than just pizza, so try some other local top dishes. Pasta, salads, calzones, sandwiches, and more can all give you something different to enjoy. 

Complete your meal with french fries, it's a great way to make dinner into a feast.

A Slice partner for one year, this restaurant is a mainstay of the community. Try them for yourself and see why they're such a local favorite. You can get your pizza to go with curbside pickup from Escas Pizza. Grab something tasty on your way home.

About the Business
Adelita's has been a realized dream, with our sole location, we attempt to capture all that charm from our home and put it on your table, a piece of Mexico, its flavor, the culture and joy of its people.

Here in adelitas its an honor to serve our guest with the highest quality service and ingredients in our dishes made from scratch. Adelita's serves your favorite Mexican dishes with the option of a quality seafood twist.

Del Frisco‚Äôs Double Eagle Steakhouse on Orlando‚Äôs famous International Drive is a must-visit while in the theme park capital of the world. The two-story Orlando restaurant features two state-of-the-art bars, five private dining rooms, a picturesque patio and a sleek, modern interior, making it the perfect place to relax and celebrate simultaneously. Featuring a diverse wine list of more than 1200 labels, diners are sure to find their inner Sommelier ‚Äì something you won‚Äôt find at any theme park.

A CULINARY ART EXPERIENCE ON INTERNATIONAL DRIVE
For over 30 years, Caf√© Tu Tu Tango has been a must-visit landmark of Orlando‚Äôs International Drive. Celebrate the fusion of art and cuisine with our vibrant collection of shareable small plates inspired by global flavors.
Take a culinary journey through our all-day menu that begins with Dips & Spreads, then explore Snack & Veggies, Meats & Seafood, Brick Oven Flat Breads and Tacos & Sliders.¬† Order like an expert and share our ‚ÄúTango Favorites‚Äù with the table including, Jamon Serrano Croquetas, Garlic Maple Chicken Wings, Crispy Brussels Sprouts and Sesame Steak Skewers.¬† Complement the experience with creative cocktails, including ‚ÄúThe Jerry‚Äù Margarita, a Banksy Smash or select our Pollock Punch to enjoy from our Non-Spirited Frescos.
Our gallery-like setting is the perfect backdrop for happy hour, brunch, lunch, or dinner. With live entertainment nightly and during brunch, Caf√© Tu Tu Tango makes dining outside of Disney worth the drive.

DINING FOR THE RIGHT SIDE OF YOUR BRAIN
Happy Hour
Happiness is‚Ä¶beers, cocktails, wines and sangrias for $5.22 and spirited cocktails for $8.22. Refuel all week long from Caf√© Tu Tu Tango‚Äôs signatures, including Black Bean Hummus, Street Corn, a Cajun Chicken Egg Roll, Cuban Slider, Grilled Fish Taco, Cauliflower Taco, Jerk Chicken Skewers, and our Triple Chocolate Cake Pops.¬† Create your small plate experience for $4.22 each, or take all eight menu items for $19.22.¬† Happy hour is available at the bar, lounge and patio every Monday through Friday from 3 pm to 6 pm.
Bottomless Brunch
Bottomless your way, every Friday ‚Äì Sunday until 3 pm at Caf√© Tu Tu Tango.¬† Take your pick from our brunch menu, plus bottomless street taco selections of chicken tinga, adobo steak, pork al pastor and vegan garbanzo tinga all for just $34.22 per person.
Add Bottomless Marys or Mimosas for $24.22.
For $46.22 per person, lean into that spirit upgrade of Mo√´t & Chandon Imp√©rial Champagne for Mimosas or Grey Goose for Bloody Marys.
Tour of Tango
Join us for the
Tour of Tango
, a guided tasting experience of signature small plates, perfect for groups of six or more. For $40.22 per person, you‚Äôll savor a selection of dishes, including dessert, with bar and beverage options available as add-ons. Get ready to embark on a culinary journey like no other!

GROUPS & EVENTS
Nestled along the vibrant heart of Orlando‚Äôs bustling International Drive for over three decades, Caf√© Tu Tu Tango stands as a cherished oasis where culinary exploration, artistic ingenuity, and sheer delight converge. Step into a realm where every dish is a canvas, and every table is a stage for shared indulgence.
Our spacious dining rooms can be transformed to create the perfect setting for all of your private event needs. Whether you are looking to host a large party or celebrate with a group of friends, we offer an experience they‚Äôll never forget. With accommodations of up to 450 guests, we have flexible seating and format options for private events, with full-service event coordination by our experienced staff members.

Rosa Mexicano
Rosa Mexicano
Authentic Mexican Cuisine
Rosa Mexicano offers a fresh take on authentic Mexican cuisine, serving both beloved classics and sophisticated dishes in a stylish and festive atmosphere. With every dish, we honor Mexican heritage, as well as the culinary techniques, global explorations, and inspirations of our founding chef, Josefina Howard. The menu features award-winning margaritas, including the Rosa Mexicano signature frozen pomegranate ‚Äì named the Best in New York City.
Reservations recommended for dinner.
Thanksgiving Specials Around the Resort

Our lively atmosphere, adorned with colorful decor and lively music, invites you to gather with friends and family for an unforgettable dining experience. About the Business
Come and experience the warmth of a family-owned restaurant where Chef Enrique Hernandez and his friends personally take care of you. Each dish is crafted with love and passion by Chef Enrique himself, ensuring an authentic culinary journey.
Our pride lies in our diverse team, hailing from various countries, bringing together a fusion of traditional Mexican flavors with unique touches from Central and South American seasonings. This blend offers our customers a wide array of delicious options to choose from.
Recognized for our friendly atmosphere, our restaurant is a place where you feel like a friend. Our entire staff provides you with a memorable dining experience, filled with joy and excellent service. Join us and savor the special flavors that make our restaurant a beloved spot for food lovers.
Visit us in Lake Mary, Florida and taste the difference that comes from a truly passionate and culturally rich kitchen. We look forward to welcoming you and making you a part of our family!

About the Business
We are a family-owned restaurant, 100% Mexican. When we moved to Orlando, we were really looking for a Mexican restaurant because we missed our food. We tried many places, but most were Tex-Mex or more Americanized. It was hard to find something truly Mexican, with authentic recipes. Then we thought, why not? Let‚Äôs create a restaurant the way it should be, with our Mexican recipes. We missed Mexico, and we wanted to show everyone what real Mexican food is like. That‚Äôs how Tacos N Grill was born.

Authentic Indian Restaurant in Orlando for Flavorful Indian Food
Know More About Us
Conveniently located near International Premium Malls and just a few miles from Universal Orlando Studios, Tabla Indian Restaurant Orlando is an award-winning choice among food places in Orlando. We specialize in Indian vegetarian cuisine, Indo-Chinese, and Thai dishes, making us one of the most versatile vegetarian restaurants in the city. Led by expert chefs, our menu celebrates subtle, complex flavors that truly capture the essence of India.
Indian Restaurant Orlando with a Wide Variety of Dishes
Our special menu promises to delight with a wide range of dishes, from Indo-Chinese specialties to Tandoori kebabs, flavorful curries, biryanis, and regional favorites like Rogan Josh. Whether you‚Äôre craving vegetarian restaurants options like dal makhani and paneer dishes or signature non-vegetarian items like butter chicken, every dish is crafted with fresh, high-quality ingredients and home-ground spices for a memorable dining experience.
Why Tabla Indian Chinese & Thai Serves the Best Indian Food in Orlando
At Tabla Indian Chinese & Thai, we‚Äôre proud to be more than just another Indian spot on International Drive. Recognized as an Indian restaurant famous for its bold flavors and authentic recipes, we‚Äôve become a must-visit for those searching for the best food places in Orlando. Here, the vibrant spices of India meet the savory touch of Chinese and the balance of Thai cuisine ‚Äî all under one roof.

About Oviedo Tabla Indian Restaurant
Craving Indian curry, Pad Thai, Gobi Manchurian, or Lamb Chops? Look no further!
At Tabla Indian Restaurant in Oviedo, we bring you the finest destination for authentic Indian and multi-cuisine dishes, preserving the true flavors of each cuisine. Whether you're in the mood for Thai food, Indo-Chinese food in Oviedo, or the best Indian food in Oviedo, Tabla is your go-to place. Located just 2 miles from the University of Central Florida, our kitchen with homestyle Indian curries feels like a home away from home for students and locals alike.
A Flavorful Journey at the Best Restaurant in Oviedo
We take pride in serving freshly cooked meals prepared to perfection. Our experienced chefs ensure that every guest leaves with a smile, satisfied by our delicious offerings. From classic vegetarian restaurant favorites to mouthwatering chicken and lamb dishes, there's something for everyone at Tabla.
Whether you‚Äôre craving flavorful Thai dishes or delicious Indo-Chinese cuisine, Tabla offers a dining experience that‚Äôs both satisfying and memorable. With a strong commitment to quality and exceptional service, it‚Äôs no surprise that we‚Äôre often recognized as the best restaurant in Oviedo. At Tabla, our success is built on authentic flavors, modernized by a team of passionate chefs who stay true to the roots of each recipe while bringing a fresh twist to every dish.

Menu of Kungfu Kitchen
The menu was updated in August, 2024.
For more information, please contact the following the location‚Äôs phone number.
Exploring Authentic Chinese Cuisine
Authentic Chinese cuisine is characterized by its rich flavors and diverse ingredients, meticulously prepared to deliver a true taste of tradition. At Kungfu Kitchen, this culinary journey begins with a focus on time-honored recipes and techniques. Each dish is crafted using methods passed down through generations, ensuring the preservation of authentic flavors. In authentic Chinese cuisine, the art of balancing flavors is emphasized. Ingredients are carefully selected and combined to achieve the perfect harmony of sweet, sour, salty, and spicy notes. Dishes such as xiao long bao and hand-pulled noodles exemplify this delicate balance, offering a genuine taste of Chinese culinary excellence.
Regional specialties are prominently featured, showcasing the diversity within Chinese cuisine. From the savory dim sum of Cantonese cuisine to the bold spices of Sichuan dishes, each region‚Äôs unique culinary traditions are represented. This variety ensures that every dining experience is a journey through different flavors and cooking styles. The emphasis on fresh, high-quality ingredients is a hallmark of authentic Chinese cooking. Vegetables are crisp, meats are tender, and seasonings are aromatic, all contributing to the vibrant taste of each dish. Techniques such as steaming, stir-frying, and braising are employed to bring out the natural flavors and textures of the ingredients. Chinese cuisine at Kungfu Kitchen provides a flavorful journey through traditional dishes and regional specialties. The dedication to preserving time-honored techniques and using fresh ingredients ensures a genuine and memorable dining experience.
Fresh Ingredients of Kungfu Kitchen
Fresh ingredients are a cornerstone of the culinary offerings at Kungfu Kitchen. The commitment to using only the highest quality produce and proteins is evident in every dish served. Vegetables are sourced from local markets to ensure optimal freshness and flavor, while meats are carefully selected for tenderness and quality. The preparation of each dish involves meticulous attention to ingredient quality. Hand-pulled noodles are made from freshly milled flour, and xiao long bao are filled with ingredients that are sourced daily to guarantee a superior taste. The freshness of the ingredients contributes to the vibrant flavors and textures that characterize Kungfu Kitchen‚Äôs menu.
Seasonal ingredients are used to enhance the flavor profile of each dish. By incorporating ingredients that are at the peak, the menu offers a dynamic and ever-changing array of options. This practice not only ensures the best possible taste but also supports sustainable sourcing practices. In summary, Kungfu Kitchen‚Äôs dedication to fresh ingredients is reflected in the exceptional quality of its dishes. By prioritizing the use of high-quality, seasonal ingredients, the restaurant delivers a dining experience that is both flavorful and authentic.
Discover the Kungfu Kitchen Menu
The menu at Kungfu Kitchen is designed to showcase a variety of authentic Chinese dishes, each prepared with careful attention to detail. Highlighted are signature items such as xiao long bao and hand-pulled noodles, which represent the best of traditional Chinese cuisine. A wide selection of dishes is offered, reflecting different regional flavors and cooking styles. The menu includes options for dim sum, main courses, and soups, providing a comprehensive taste of Chinese culinary traditions. Special attention is given to the preparation of each dish to ensure the authenticity of flavors and presentation. The menu is crafted to accommodate various dining preferences, from light appetizers to hearty main courses. Seasonal specials are featured to highlight the use of fresh, local ingredients and offer a dynamic dining experience. The balance of traditional and innovative dishes ensures that each visit presents a new and exciting culinary adventure. Kungfu Kitchen menu provides a diverse array of authentic Chinese dishes, with a focus on quality ingredients and traditional preparation methods. The thoughtfully curated selection allows diners to explore a wide range of flavors and enjoy an authentic taste of Chinese cuisine.

Green House Chinese Restaurant is a family operated restaurant in Orlando that offers a wide variety of Chinese food. Our recipes originate from the Mainland, Hong Kong and Canton provinces. We specialize in Cantonese/Hong Kong cuisine and our menu selection is designed to cater to all tastes. Our services are available for dine in, take out, delivery and even catering.

Menu
Fresh and Casual Korean Food in Orlando
Here's a look at our menu! It's filled with all our family's favorite Korean dishes, from comforting soups to sizzling BBQ. We hope you find something you'll love while you're here in Orlando.
Always Fresh, Always Good
We have a simple rule in our kitchen: use good ingredients. We pick fresh veggies and use high-quality prime meats in all our cooking. Since we make everything to order, your food is always served fresh and full of flavor.
Find Your Favorite Dish
Take a look around our menu and find your next favorite meal. We're excited to cook for you and your family!
Why You'll Love Our Food
We cook the kind of food we'd be excited to eat ourselves! Our goal is simply to serve up tasty, authentic Korean dishes that keep you coming back for more.

MAKE A RESERVATION FOR HIBACHI LAKE BUENA VISTA
ABOUT OUR HIBACHI RESTAURANT IN LAKE BUENA VISTA
Kobe Japanese Steakhouse is the best Hibachi Lake Buena Vista has to offer. We give our guests an authentic Teppanyaki dining experience along with the fun of Hibachi cooking.
Come dine on signature dishes like the high-end Ultimate Japanese Wagyu or our hand-made sushi rolls like the Spicy Tuna Poke Bowl. Pair your meal with a refreshing Passion Fruit Margarita or split a
Scorpion Bowl
with your group. For those with certain food allergies, we have a variety of gluten-free & vegan options too!
Get interactive with your dinner at our famous Hibachi show. Our world class chefs are trained in the art of Hibachi cooking and will keep you and your family amazed and entertained throughout your dining experience with us. They‚Äôll delight you with tricks like the Beating Heart, the Egg Roll, and the signature Onion Volcano!
Read More +
We‚Äôre open for lunch too. Come enjoy one of our
signature sushi rolls
before you head to the parks or Disney Springs for the afternoon.
In a hurry? Order Online here for pick-up!
It‚Äôs the Hibachi Lake Buena Vista has been enjoying and coming back to time and again Book your reservation below!
How to Find Us
From I-4: Take exit 68 for Route 535 and head North towards the entrance for Disney. Pass the entrance and take your first right on Palm Parkway. Take your third right into the shopping center and we are on your left!

Have your party gathered around the grill to enjoy delicious, authentic Japanese food while enjoying the show. Unsure what to do for lunch? Stop in for a guaranteed fun time. Book Today!
Due to our unique communal seating arrangement, please expect a short wait time with your reservation upon checking in with a complete party.
An automatic 18% service charge will be applied to all checks. 100% of service charge is paid out to our employees.
Private tables can be requested by smaller parties. There is a $500 spending minimum for each private table reserved.
We offer limited online booking availability, with communal seating, for large parties 11-20.
For parties 20+ or large parties requesting a booking outside of online availability, please contact your preferred Kobe location by completing our online
inquiry form
to reserve through a manager with a banquet menu. We cannot guarantee that reservations booked separately will be sat together.

Walala's Mouth Watering Menu
Craving the best hand-pulled noodles in Orlando? Your search ends here!
At Wa La La, we bring the heart of traditional Chinese street food to your table with our signature
Lanzhou Hand Pulled Noodles
(ÂÖ∞Â∑ûÊâãÂ∑•ÊãâÈù¢). Each strand is expertly pulled to order, ensuring a fresh, chewy texture that perfectly captures our rich, slow-cooked broths.
From the iconic Hand-pulled Noodles with Large Sliced Beef Shank to the fiery kick of our Spicy Sliced Beef Shank Noodles, and the comforting Dan Dan Noodles, every dish is a culinary journey.
Experience the authentic taste of China right here in Orlando
, with options like savory braised beef, tender shredded chicken, and flavorful vegetarian noodles. Whether you‚Äôre seeking a classic beef noodle soup or a tantalizing dry noodle dish, Wa La La Hand Pulled Noodles offers an unforgettable taste of tradition and skill. Dive into a bowl of Orlando‚Äôs most talked-about noodles today!

Sashimi and Nigiri
Sashimi (which translates into pierced meat) is typically raw, premium cut fish that can be dipped in shoyu and wasabi. However, not all sashimi is served raw. Tataki, a popular form of sashimi, is made by searing a slice of fish on the outside and then dipping the meat into a vinegar mixture before serving. About Durian Durian
With more than 20 combined years of foodservice and restaurant experience, we focus on authentic Southeast Asian cuisine prepared with fresh ingredients to create balanced dishes that are deliciously refreshing. Durian Durian is at the heart of Lake Nona, where we intend to be a comfortable, neighborhood restaurant that serves excellent, fresh, and creative Thai food at affordable prices. You are guaranteed to enjoy your experience.

Where We Started
Our Story
China Pearl Restaurant offers authentic and delicious-tasting Chinese cuisine in Clermont, FL. China Pearl's convenient location and affordable prices make our restaurant a natural choice for dine-in or take-out meals in the Clermont community. Our restaurant is known for its variety of tastes and high-quality fresh ingredients. Come and experience our friendly atmosphere and excellent service.

What our customers say
Reviews
We have ordered takeout here a couple of times. They are always timely in preparing the order, every order has been correctly made and delicious. We love the Hot & Spicy Chicken, Pepper Steak, and Lo Mein. So good!
Richard W.
We are new here in Clermont and tried this place for the first time, and they did not disappoint! My partner and I had their General Tso's Chicken,  Mongolian Beef, and Coconut Shrimp. It was absolutely amazing! We will be back for sure.
Shelby O.
My family and I had a fantastic experience here. The service was amazing, the food came out hot and perfectly cooked and was so delicious. We are so grateful we chose to eat here, it made our night.
Brandon V.
I tried the house special chow mei fun and orange chicken with spring roll and wonton for an appetizer! Delicious food! Definitely taste homemade and fresh! Great proportions and price!
Tom F.
Picked up our first takeout order tonight, it was ready on time, packed well, hot, and had some of the tastiest Chinese food we've had. Would 100% recommend them and will definitely be back.
Carol C.
By far my favorite restaurant! You can order for pick up or have them delivered. Either way, you get your money's worth and it is delicious food! I have never had to wait long to get my order, and they are always punctual and polite.
Francis U.

U & Me Revolving Hot Pot menu
Flavors That Delight
Each of U & Me‚Äôs broth options is carefully crafted to deliver a depth of flavor that tantalizes the taste buds. From the classic and comforting flavors of a traditional bone broth to the aromatic and spicy profiles of Sichuan and Thai broths, U & Me have something to satisfy every palate.
For those seeking a bold and robust taste, U & Me‚Äôs broth selection includes options such as a rich beef broth infused with herbs and spices, or a hearty mushroom broth that imparts earthy flavors. These broths create a savory foundation for your hot pot experience, allowing the ingredients to soak up the delicious essence and enhance their natural flavors.
Exquisite BoBa Tea Experience
BoBa Tea, also known as Bubble Tea, has become a beloved and trendy beverage enjoyed by people of all ages around the world. With its delightful combination of tea, chewy tapioca pearls, and a range of flavorful toppings, BoBa Tea offers a unique and refreshing experience.
The highlight of BoBa Tea lies in the addition of chewy tapioca pearls, which add a playful and satisfying element to each sip. These tapioca pearls, often referred to as ‚Äúboba,‚Äù are made from cassava starch and are cooked until they achieve the perfect consistency‚Äîsoft and chewy, yet not overly mushy. Their unique texture provides a delightful contrast to the smoothness of the tea, creating a pleasurable and fun drinking experience.
Let‚Äôs Try U & Me‚Äôs Menu
Choice of broth
Lunch Combo Special
Drinks
Customers have the option to choose from a selection of five different hot pot broths, including Original, Pork Bone, Spicy, Herbal, Tomato, Mushroom, and Tom Yum. Each broth offers a unique flavor and combination of ingredients, providing a variety of delicious options to suit any palate. Whether you prefer a mild and savory taste or a spicy and tangy kick, U & Me‚Äôs hot pot menu has something for everyone.
We are thrilled to offer you a selection of five Lunch Combo Special. Choose your favorite from the images below and indulge in a delightful culinary experience like no other.
At our establishment, you‚Äôll find a diverse range of drinks to choose from. Whether you‚Äôre in the mood for a smoothie, a boba tea or beer, we have an extensive drink menu that caters to all preferences.

Make a Reservation for Hibachi Near UCF
Our Alafaya Hibachi Restaurant (Near UCF)
Kobe Japanese Steakhouse is the best Hibachi Alafaya, FL has to offer. We give our guests an authentic Teppanyaki dining experience along with the fun of Hibachi.
Get interactive with your dinner with our famous Hibachi show. Our world class chefs are trained in the art of Hibachi cooking and will keep you and your family amazed and entertained throughout your dining experience with us. They‚Äôll delight you with tricks like the Beating Heart, the Egg Roll, and the signature Onion Volcano! Enjoy signature dishes such as the Kobe Trio. So, if you‚Äôre in the Alafaya area, stop in for a Hibachi show!
Read More +
Come dine on signature dishes like our hand-made Red Dragon Roll and the Spicy Tuna Poke Bowl. Pair your meal with a refreshing Kobe Breeze or split a Scorpion Bowl with your friends. For those with certain food allergies, we have a variety of gluten-free & vegan options too!
We‚Äôre open for lunch too. Come enjoy one of our signature sushi rolls like the Rainbow Roll before you head back to class.
In a hurry? Order Online for fast pick-up!
It‚Äôs the best Hibachi near UCF that students can‚Äôt get enough of! Book your reservation below!
Looking for another location? We‚Äôre also located in
Altamonte Springs
,
Longwood
and
Kirkman/Universal
How to Find Our Alafaya Japanese Restaurant
From UCF: Take Alafaya Drive South towards Avalon Park. Make a right on East Colonial Drive and we are a quarter mile down on the right-hand side.

Save the date for any number of special occasions: Birthday parties, graduations, anniversaries, and more. Gather your party around the grill to enjoy delicious, authentic Japanese food and watch the show. Unsure what to do for lunch? Stop in for a guaranteed fun time. Book Today!
Due to our unique communal seating arrangement, please expect a short wait time with your reservation upon checking in with a complete party.
An automatic 18% service charge will be applied to all checks. 100% of service charge is paid out to our employees.
Private tables can be requested by smaller parties. There is a $450 spending minimum for each private table reserved.
We offer limited online booking availability, with communal seating, for large parties 11-20.
For parties 20+ or large parties requesting a booking outside of online availability, please contact your preferred Kobe location by completing our online
inquiry form
to reserve through a manager with a banquet menu. We cannot guarantee that reservations booked separately will be sat together.

Where We Started
Our Story
China Taste Restaurant offers authentic and delicious tasting Chinese cuisine in St Cloud, FL. China Taste's convenient location and affordable prices make our restaurant a natural choice for eat-in or take-out meals in the St Cloud community. Our restaurant is known for its variety of tastes and high quality fresh ingredients. Come and experience our friendly atmosphere and excellent service.

What our customers say
Reviews
This restaurant has the most delicious, and tasty dish, I have had anywhere. I love their food. Cooked perfectly, and timely. The cook is the BEST! The guy up front is nice and sociable.
Sandy Romkey
Stopped in for lunch while on a road trip. The food was delicious, fast, and fresh. The prices were fair and portions were HUGE. I will definitely stop by next time I am in this part of Florida!
Rachel Rhoat
Completely caught me off guard and exceeded my expectations. We took a chance with China Taste. Cashew Chicken, wings and pork chow mein were all wonderful.
Jefferson Cosgrove
Best chinese in town. Their chicken is so delicious, the texture is soooo good and that sauce on the general tsos and sesame is delicious. Fried rice is also very very good.
Kevin ONeil
Best Chinese takeout I‚Äôve ever had. They are generous with the amount of meat in their fried rice and lo mein. Everything was of great quality and delicious. Portions are generous.
Laura C.
I've tried most of the Chinese food restaurants in st cloud, and this is by far my favorite. Their portions are extremely generous, staff is always friendly, and the food tastes great.
Christina Amato

The Food
Asian street food is special. The flavors are bold and unapologetic, the recipes are passed down from generation to generation, and the wok technique is unparalleled. The best Asian street food mesmerizes all five senses: sight, smell, sound, touch, and of course, taste. Don‚Äôt believe us? Try it for yourself.
Item availability may vary by location.
Consuming raw or undercooked meats, poultry, seafood, shellfish, or eggs may increase your risk of foodborne illness. Please inform your server if you have any food allergies.

Saigon Noodle & Grill was spotted by Guy Fieri, the mayor of Flavor town and chosen to be Featured on The Food Network Channel: Diner's Drive-Ins & Dives.
‚Äã
The Restaurant is located in the heart of Orlando‚Äôs Milk District, between Bumby avenue and Washington street. Saigon Noodle & Grill is embracing the contemporary of Vietnamese cuisine and managing to deliver one of Orlando's favorite dining experiences, with its relaxed and welcoming attentive service.
Open for breakfast, brunch, lunch and dinner, offering outdoor and indoor seating with a very own private room, Saigon Noodle & Grill can deliver an array of dining experiences from breakfasts to after-work drinks, to formal special events.
‚Äã
Our restaurant specialties include Vietnamese Beef Pho Soup, Vermicelli Noodle, Rice Platter, Pan-Fried Noodle, and Family Style entrees. We are also famous for our Vietnamese Iced Milk Coffee and a great selection of Asian Beers.

About the Business
Business owner information
Tim L.
Business Owner
the seafood at mikado sushi metrowest location comes air-shipped via the tokyo toyosu  market,we have a unique fusion approach that focuses on exotic ingredients and we applying traditional Japanese cooking methods and ingredients, then blend them with techniques and ingredients from other cultures such as Thai ingredients, Italian inspired Sauce as well as a vast variety of ingredients from all over Asia. Sourcing local farm-to-table produce will allow us to achieve the quality nutritional values and achieve the flavors of a fresh product. Our teams methods result with flavor combinations that are quite unique and our culture will create an interactive customer experience with health, nutrition and cuisine. 
our flavors can go from bold to subtle, our plates can be simple sushi specialties, .like japan fresh japanese hamachi with light jilapeno in house made garlic ponzu , bluefin tuna taretar on crispy wasabi nori . freshest sashimi ranges from dark sea eel to sea urchin . For rolls, we created an exceptionally good combo of fish, crunch, spice, and healthy vegetable . Hot entrees depart from the standard with options like the grill seafood teriyaki ,pad thai noodle , cod fish with garlic sauce, or enjoy our Chefs showcase of the freshest fish from the world's finest markets like tokyo , Hawaii, Hokkaido and of course we will always source local sources as a means of providing our customers with local flavors

Bulgogi Fries
Thinly sliced USDA select certified marinated beef piled on our seasoned fries topped with mozzarella cheese, a spicy mayo drizzle, and chopped green onions.
Potstickers
Pork or Vegetable
Lightly fried pork or vegetable dumplings brushed with Bonchon Signature Sauce. Choice of Soy Garlic, Spicy, or Half & Half.
Shrimp Shumai
Steamed or fried shrimp dumplings drizzled with spicy mayo & soy garlic sauces.
Takoyaki
Fried octopus dumplings drizzled with Kewpie Mayo, katsu sauce and sprinkled with scallions.
Bao Buns
Three steamed buns with cucumbers, coleslaw, spicy mayo and katsu sauce. Your choice of Pork Belly, Fried Chicken, or Bulgogi. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Korean Tacos
Bulgogi Spicy Chicken
Choice of spicy chicken or marinated ribeye over three flour tortillas. Topped with lettuce, coleslaw, buttermilk ranch, spicy mayo, and scallions. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Popcorn Shrimp
With choice of Cucumber Wasabi or Spicy Mayo. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Edamame
Steamed soybeans sprinkled with salt.
Main Dishes
Your Korean favorites with our signature Bonchon flare. Taste Korean cuisine in a fresh and delicious way.
Order Now
Bulgogi
Thinly sliced USDA select certified marinated beef, saut√©ed with mushrooms, scallions, sesame seeds, and onions. Served with white rice. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Japchae
Glass noodles, red pepper, carrots, onions, spinach, mushrooms, and bulgogi stir-fried with Soy Garlic sauce and sesame oil topped with sesame seeds. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Chicken Katsu
Breaded chicken cutlet served with steamed rice, and drizzled with katsu sauce and spicy mayo. Served with coleslaw on the side. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Tteokbokki
Rice cakes simmered in spicy broth with fish cakes, scallions, and onions topped with mozzarella cheese and vegetable potstickers. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Buldak
Spicy chicken, rice cakes, onions, and hot pepper sauce stir-fried and topped with scallions and sesame seeds, and mozzarella cheese. Served with white rice. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
House Fried Rice
Chicken Bulgogi Kimchi Bacon Plain
A traditional wok-prepared dish with your choice of our famous Soy Garlic chicken, Spicy chicken, or marinated ribeye with Jasmine rice, fresh vegetables, and fried egg topped with sesame seeds and a cucumber garnish. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Bibimbap
Bulgogi Chicken (Soy Garlic or Spicy) Plain Tofu
Rice with scrambled egg, lettuce, carrots, saut√©ed onions, spinach and mushrooms. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Udon Noodle Soup
Bulgogi Fried Egg Plain
Thick wheat noodles served in a savory broth with mushrooms. Topped with scallions. *Contains sesame seeds or sesame seed oil.
Sides
Our delicious and savory sides pair perfectly with any of our fried chicken, starters or main dishes.
Order Now
French Fries
Premium potatoes, perfectly fried to a crispy golden brown on the outside with soft, fluffy comfort on the inside. Lightly seasoned with high-quality salt, they‚Äôre an ideal complement to any meal or a savory snack on the go!
Seasoned Fries
Crispy and golden, perfectly fried on the outside and taken to the next level with garlic seasoning, parmesan cheese, and parsley flakes. Each bite is packed with bold, savory flavor that makes these fries the perfect side or a delicious snack!
Onion Rings
Onions, lightly battered and fried to golden perfection, with a seriously crunchy outside and a delicious, tender, and flavorful inside. Pair them with a Bonchon dipping sauce for the ultimate taste experience.
Coleslaw
Crisp cabbage and shredded carrots dressed in a creamy sauce. Bonchon Coleslaw blends a delicate, slightly sweet tang with a satisfyingly crunchy texture that you won‚Äôt soon forget.
Kimchi
Fermented vegetables and cabbage, salted and seasoned with a bold blend of spices. This iconic staple of Korean culture delivers a salty, sour, and spicy kick to any of our main dishes.
Pickled Radish
Daikon radish, chopped into small cubes and pickled in a sweet, sour, and lightly salty brine, is a staple of the Korean table. Pickled radish is supremely crunchy and a refreshing companion to any dish.
Steamed Rice
Fluffy, white grains provide a neutral flavor base for any dish. A classic addition, it pairs effortlessly with bold Korean flavors. Try adding any of our sauces to delight your tastebuds.
Desserts
Korean Donuts
Two traditional soft and fluffy Korean donuts coated with cinnamon and sugar on the outside, served with a sweet cream dipping sauce.

About the Business
Discover a unique dining experience where the bold flavors of Chinese cuisine meet the vibrant spices of Thai dishes and the comforting warmth of authentic ramen. Our menu offers a diverse selection of traditional Chinese favorites, from savory stir-fries and dumplings to aromatic noodle and rice dishes. Complementing this, we feature classic Thai specialties such as rich curries, tangy stir-fries, and refreshing salads, each crafted with fresh herbs and spices. For noodle lovers, our hearty ramen bowls provide a perfect blend of flavorful broths, tender noodles, and premium toppings. Whether you‚Äôre craving the comfort of Chinese home-style cooking, the zest of Thai flavors, or a steaming bowl of ramen, our restaurant brings it all together under one roof.

ABOUT OUR HIBACHI RESTAURANT NEAR UNIVERSAL STUDIOS (KIRKMAN LOCATION)
Kobe Japanese Steakhouse is the best Asian restaurant with Hibachi near Universal Studios, FL. We offer an authentic Teppanyaki dining experience along with the fun of Hibachi cooking.
Come dine on specialized dishes like our fan-favorite Kobe Trio or the fresh Yum Yum Shrimp! Wash it down with a fruity Mt. Fuji or our twist on a classic drink, a Nagasaki Old Fashioned. And for those with certain food allergies, we have a variety of gluten-free & vegan options too!
Looking for the ultimate interactive dining experience near Universal? Reserve our famous Hibachi show! Our world class chefs are trained in the art of Hibachi cooking and will keep you and your family amazed and entertained throughout your dining experience with us. They‚Äôll delight you with tricks like the Beating Heart, the Egg Roll, and the signature Onion Volcano!
Read More +
We‚Äôre open for lunch too. Come enjoy one of our signature sushi rolls like the Red Dragon Roll before heading back off to the parks (or to the office) for the afternoon.
Need to grab-n-go? Order Online for pick-up!
Ready to sink your teeth into delicious, authentic Japanese cuisine? Come on in for the best hibachi Kirkman Road has to offer! Book your reservation below and get ready for a night of great fun and full bellies.
Looking for another location? We‚Äôre also located in
I-Drive/Convention
,
Lake Buena Vist
a and
Celebration/Kissimmee
How to Find Us
If you‚Äôre coming from I-4, take Exit 75B for Kirkman and keep right. After the first light where Universal is on your left, it will be after the DoubleTree Hotel on your right.
If you‚Äôre coming from inside Universal, take Tom Williams Way out to the light and turn left. It will be after the DoubleTree Hotel on your right.

Get some time away from the parks, but still have world class entertainment right up close for lunch! Secure your booking today!
Due to our unique communal seating arrangement, please expect a short wait time with your reservation upon checking in with a complete party.
An automatic 18% service charge will be applied to all checks. 100% of service charge is paid out to our employees.
Private tables can be requested by smaller parties. There is a $500 spending minimum for each private table reserved.

inquiry form

About the Business
Business owner information
Bruno F.
Business Owner
Nouveau- American restaurant, offering pre-fix chef's table dinner experiences with a new menu monthly.

We invite you to experience the art of fine dining, where every dish is carefully crafted by our skilled culinary team. Our mission is to provide you with an elegant and welcoming experience, from the moment you step into our restaurant. We take pride in sourcing the freshest and finest ingredients, and each dish is a harmonious blend of flavors and textures. 

To complement and elevate your dining experience, we offer a selection of curated wine pairings, chosen by our sommelier. From rare vintages to new and exciting labels, our wine list features a diverse range of options to suit every palate.

 Join us for a memorable culinary journey that will leave you with unforgettable flavors and memories.

DRESS CODE
In order to deliver the best experience to you in our upscale, sophisticated environment, appropriate dress is required after 4pm.
Thank you for not wearing gym attire, track suits, tank tops, beach wear, flip flops, outfits with exposed undergarments, and clothing with offensive words or images.
Dress shorts with dress shoes are allowed on all of our patios and cafe seating areas, but not in the main dining room. We do not consider cargo shorts, cut-off jeans, or surfer shorts, dress shorts.
We reserve the right to refuse entry and service at The H, including but not limited to guests who do not adhere to our dress-code guidelines.

Lunch
Enjoy Keke's Breakfast Cafe lunch menu featuring grilled paninis like cheese steak and portabella, sandwiches and wraps such as BLT, cheeseburger, turkey club, and chicken Caesar, crisp salads with fresh fruits, and sides including french fries and onion rings. Gluten-free and vegetarian selections available! Served after 10:30 a.m.
Beverages
Indulge in Keke's Breakfast Cafe beverages menu, featuring fresh hot coffee, iced drinks, juices, milk, hot chocolate, and signature cocktails like classic mimosas, white peach bellinis, and wildberry sangria. Gluten-free and vegetarian options available!

Where Flavor Meets Fresh
At Bolay Fresh Bold Kitchen, we're flipping the script on healthy eating. Gone are the days of bland, ho-hum meals that make wellness feel like a chore. Here, we're all about making the wholesome downright irresistible. Our secret? Marrying dazzling flavors with peak freshness in every bite. With us, healthy doesn't just mean greens and grains, but a vivid palette of ingredients that dance on your palate. At Bolay, we're proving that 'delicious' and 'nutritious' aren't just pals; they're soulmates.
Bolay
Menu
Bolay Fresh Bold Kitchen is the perfect mix between vibrant flavor¬†and a healthier life.
Who wants healthy food to be boring? Every single dish on our menu is 100% gluten-free and seasoned with care, crafting a top-tier Bol experience.
Whipped up fresh every morning right inside our kitchen, Bolay's flavors stack up to guarantee a mouthful of delight with every bite. We are proud to be an allergen-friendly haven, our mantra is simple: gluten-free, always.
Because here at Bolay, we're not just serving food; we're welcoming every guest into our family, offering the crispest, healthiest eats around.

Helena Modern Riviera Main Menu
Each Dish is a tribute to the serene luxury and vibrant
tastes of the Mediterranean and French Riviera
Helena pays homage to the contemporary Riviera restaurants flourishing along the Mediterranean coast. With a laid-back atmosphere infused with coastal Balinese vibes, we offer a fusion of Mediterranean and American cuisine. Our menu is an ode to freshness and flavor, featuring handcrafted cocktails that will tantalize your taste buds. Join us and savor the best of both worlds as we blend Mediterranean traditions with American innovation.

Traditional Brunch Menu
Indulge in a mouthwatering traditional menu at Another Broken Egg Cafe. From crispy chicken & waffles to delectable eggs benedict, savory shrimp'n'grits, and customizable omelettes, our breakfast and brunch options are sure to satisfy your cravings. Visit us today and experience the ultimate breakfast delight!
Brunch Specialties
Add a Sweet Temptations flavor pancake.
Chicken & Waffles
Crispy fried chicken tenders on a Belgian waffle, drizzled with house-made chipotle honey.
Cinnamon Roll French Toast
Thick-sliced, house-baked French-toast style cinnamon rolls topped with cream cheese icing, rum butter sauce drizzle, fresh seasonal berries and whipped cream.
Country Power Bowl
Scrambled eggs filled with country ham, onions and tomatoes over Cheddar Jack cheese grits. Topped with country sausage gravy. Served with baked bacon and an over-sized biscuit. (1370 cal)
Pair with an Abita¬Æ Amber Lager (130 cal) and Rwanda Single-Origin Coffee (0 cal).
Crab Cake Benedict
Jumbo lump crab cakes on an English muffin, topped with poached eggs, andouille-infused hollandaise, red peppers and green onions.
Eggs Blackstone Benedict
Grilled red tomato slices on an English muffin, topped with poached eggs, hollandaise, chopped bacon and green onions.
Hash Brown Benedict
Ham and cheese stuffed crispy hash brown croquettes, topped with poached eggs, mushroom herbed hollandaise and red peppers. Served with grits or fresh country potatoes
Mardi Gras Omelette
Filled with Louisiana crawfish, gulf shrimp, andouille and red peppers, topped with tomato hollandaise, tomatoes and green onions.
Shrimp 'N Grits
Gulf shrimp and andouille sausage sauteed with red peppers and onions in a spicy low country reduction, over creamy cheese grits.  Served with garlic bread and a lemon.
Smoked Salmon Benedict
Toasted bagel, cream cheese, smoked salmon and poached eggs, topped with red onions, capers and green onions.
Sensible Creations
Monterey Power Omelette
Egg white omelette with chicken, onions, green chilies and tomatoes. Topped with guajillo sauce, Jack cheese and avocado. Side of sour cream. Served with an English muffin and fresh seasonal fruit.
Shrimp Benedict
Poached eggs on grilled focaccia with saut√©ed mushrooms, roasted peppers, onions and arugula.  Topped with Gulf shrimp in a creamy velout√© sauce and sliced green onions. Served with fresh seasonal fruit.
Skinny Omelette
Goat cheese-filled egg white omelette with asparagus, roasted red peppers and roasted garlic cloves. Topped with fresh herbs and green onions. Served with an English muffin and fresh seasonal fruit.
Indulgences
Served with two eggs any style and your choice of meat.
Apple Fritter French Toast
French-toast style fritters, fried apples, rum butter sauce, blueberries, powdered sugar (1849 cal). With two eggs any style (+120-220 cal) & bacon or sausage patties (+180/250 cal)
Belgian Waffle
Light and golden waffle topped with powdered sugar
Bourbon Street Pancakes
Three house-recipe cakes topped bananas, pecans, rum butter sauce drizzle and whipped cream.
Buttermilk Pancakes
Three house-recipe buttermilk cakes.
Classic French Toast
Thick-sliced bread battered and grilled, topped with powdered sugar
Cookie Dough Waffle
Freshly-baked cookie dough Belgian waffle topped with cookie dough bites, fresh whipped cream, chocolate drizzle and powdered sugar. Served with two eggs any style and baked bacon or house-made sausage patties.
Lemon Blueberry Goat Cheese Pancakes
Three house-recipe cakes with fresh blueberries and goat cheese, topped with lemon zest and fresh whipped cream.
Strawberry Pound Cake French Toast
French toast-style pound cake topped with fresh strawberries, fresh whipped cream and cr√®me br√ªl√©e sugar
Omelettes and Scramblers
Served with an English muffin and grits or fresh country potatoes.  Substitute fresh fruit or City Grits.
Bacquezo¬Æ Omelette
Cream cheese-filled omelette with bacon, topped with garlic butter saut√©ed chorizo, Jack cheese and green onions.
Hey Lucy!¬Æ Omelette
Chorizo, onions and green chilies omelette, topped with Cheddar Jack cheese and avocado. Sides of salsa and sour cream.
Lobster & Brie Omelette
Cream cheese-filled omelette topped with Brie cheese and champagne butter sauce saut√©ed lobster meat, tomatoes and green onions. Served with an English muffin.
Southwest Scrambler
Scrambled eggs filled with chorizo, onions, tomatoes and green chilies, topped with Cheddar Jack cheese. Sides of guacamole and salsa. Served with flour tortillas instead of an English muffin.
Sunrise Spinach Scrambler
Scrambled eggs filled with fresh spinach, bacon and onions, topped with Jack cheese.
The Floridian‚Ñ¢ Omelette
Cream cheese-filled omelette topped with garlic butter saut√©ed crab meat, Jack cheese and green onions
The Supreme Omelette
Filled with sausage, bacon, onions and mushrooms, topped with Cheddar Jack cheese.
Veggie Delight Omelette
Goat cheese-filled omelette with fresh spinach, tomatoes and saut√©ed mushrooms. Served with an English muffin and grits or fresh country potatoes.
Traditional Classics
Served with an English muffin and grits or fresh country potatoes. Substitute fresh fruit or City Grits.
Biscuit & Gravy
House-recipe country sausage over an over-sized biscuit, two eggs any style, and two house-made sausage patties.
BROKEN EGG¬Æ Biscuit Sandwich
Fried chicken tender and a BROKEN EGG¬Æ topped with country sausage gravy on an over-sized biscuit.
Eggs Benedict
Grilled breakfast ham on an English muffin, topped with poached eggs, hollandaise and green onions.
Huevos Rancheros
Crispy flour tortillas, black beans, green chilies, onions and two over-medium eggs with Cheddar Jack cheese and cilantro.  Sides of salsa and sour cream.
Traditional Day Starter
Two eggs any style with your choice of baked bacon, house-made sausage patties, andouille sausage, maple apple chicken sausage or sweet ham.  Served with an English muffin.
Sandwiches & Salads
Burgers and sandwiches served with a pickle & country potatoes.
Bacon Lover's BLT&A
Thick-cut baked bacon strips, lettuce, avocado, tomatoes and Cheddar Jack cheese with garlic aioli on nine-grain bread.
Benedict Burger
Hand-pressed beef patty, grilled ham, over-medium fried egg, hollandaise and green onions on a brioche bun.
Blackened Shrimp Salad
Mixed greens, blackened shrimp, tomato, cucumber, scallions, pineapple, pickled red onions, parmesan cheese crisps, honey jalepe√±o vinaigrette.
Brunch Jambalaya
Shrimp, crawfish and andouille sausage in a spiced bell pepper, onion and celery rice saut√©. Topped with two eggs any style (+120-220 cal).
Chicken Salad Sandwich
All-white meat chicken salad, lettuce, tomato, nine-grain bread. Served with fresh country potatoes and a pickle spear.
Chicken Tortilla Soup
Roasted all-white meat chicken, corn, black beans, tomato broth, crispy tortilla strips, diced tomatoes, cilantro.
Classic Bacon Burger
Two hand-pressed beef patties, baked bacon, Cheddar Jack cheese, lettuce, tomato and red onion on a brioche bun.  Served with a pickle and fresh country potatoes.
Louisiana Gumbo
Louisiana-style gumbo, shrimp, crab, crawfish, jambalaya rice, green onions. With focaccia bread
Sonoma Club Sandwich
Ham, turkey, baked bacon, guacamole, Cheddar Jack cheese, tomato and pickled red onions on your choice of white or nine-grain bread.
Southern Chicken Sandwich
Choice of grilled or fried chicken, baked bacon, avocado, lettuce, tomato and pickled red onions with ranch dressing on a brioche bun.
Southern Fried Chicken Salad
Mixed greens, fried chicken tenders, sliced hardboiled egg, tomato, bacon bits, pickled red onions, honey mustard dressing.

Additional Information
Conveniently located inside Universal Studios CityWalk in Orlando, Bubba Gump Shrimp Co. is family-friendly and open to walk ins. Stop by for great food and a good time.
Bubba Gump Shrimp Co. captures the charm and American spirit that made ‚ÄúForrest Gump‚Äù a smash hit, featuring down-home d√©cor reminiscent of the movie‚Äôs setting in Alabama. Now branded as an American icon, the restaurant showcases memorabilia and still-photos from the movie, along with reproductions of script pages, storyboards and even some costumes.
At our core, we are a seafood restaurant committed to providing a casual environment where everyone can enjoy a great meal and have some fun too.
Food is the hero at the Bubba Gump Shrimp Co., we serve food that makes our employees proud and will make you want to return. Our menu features shrimp, of course. And once you've had one of our margaritas hand-shaken at your table, you're sure to be a fan.
At Bubba Gump Shrimp Co. we‚Äôre always ready for great food, great fun, and a great party!

About Us
FROM HUMBLE BEGINNINGS‚Ä¶
Cafe Mineiro Brazilian Steakhouse, strives to be the premier family Brazilian steakhouse restaurant in the mid-price casual dining range of the Centre Region. Our main focus is serving quality food at a great value. Cafe Mineiro Brazilian Steakhouse philosophy can be stated simply; we want you to have a wonderful family-friendly dining experience. Every member of the staff shares this sentiment ‚Äì from the front door to the kitchen door. Our guests are our reason for existence; without them there would't be Cafe Mineiro Brazilian Steakhouse.

The Menu
Grill
Beef
Maminha **
GF
This Tri-tip sirloin steak is unique to Rodizio Grill, the Brazilian steakhouse. This steak is a moderate marbled-to-lean cut, which makes it a very flavorful steak. It's our Founder‚Äôs favorite! This cut is best if consumed medium to medium rare.
Fraldinha **
GF
Fraldinha, beef tender, is tender and robust in flavor - one of the most distinctive cuts of beef enjoyed in Southern Brazil. Pairs perfectly with our homemade chimichurri sauce.
Bife com Parmes√£o **
GF
This Parmesan sirloin steak is unique to Rodizio Grill. It is lean, tender and topped with fresh Parmesan cheese.
Picanha **
GF
This top sirloin (beef top sirloin cap, sirloin cap, sirloin culotte) is our signature cut, specially trimmed and prepared to assure final product perfection.
Bife Com Alho **
GF
Bife com Alho is a tender cut of beef basted with our traditional house garlic rub. Our Rodizio gauchos baste the beef with a special garlic butter recipe that infuses garlic flavor into the beef. When you bite into Bife com Alho, you can taste a delicate, not overwhelming, garlic flavor.
Chef's Special **
GF
Several meats and other local selections are served as Rodizio Grill Chef's Special items and are not available at all locations at all times. Please contact your local Rodizio Grill for current Chef's Specials.
Poultry
Frango Com Bacon
GF
Frango com Bacon, chicken wrapped in bacon, is a Rodizio Grill guest and staff favorite. Tender, juicy chicken breast is wrapped in savory bacon and grilled to perfection.
Galeto
GF
Galeto is our slow-roasted, bone-in chicken thigh. Marinated  overnight in wine and a special fresh herb blend (Vinha d'alho), this grilled feature boasts crispy savory outside, and perfectly tender meat inside.
Frango Agri-Doce
GF
Rodizio Grill puts a spin on the traditional churrasco with this crowd pleasing sweet and spicy chicken.  Frango Agri-Doce was created in the kitchens of Rodizio Grill to attend to guests requests for a flavorful chicken option. The chicken is basted in Rodizio Grill's unique home-made gaucho sauce, then grilled to bring out the flavors.
Cora√ß√£o de Frango Temperado
GF
Cora√ß√£o de Frango Temperado is one of Brazil's favorite "Churrasco" appetizers.
Chicken hearts were traditionally found gracing in the first "Churrascarias" in southern Brazil. Chicken hearts, though different in texture, are very flavorful.
Pork
Lingui√ßa
GF
Lingui√ßa a very mild and flavorful Brazilian sausage. With a special MSG free Rodizio Grill recipe, this sausage is great right off the grill or as part of our Feijoada, our traditional Brazilian black bean stew found in the hot dishes section of our gourmet salad bar.
Pernil
GF
This flavorful selection of Berkshire Pork is lightly salted and perfectly grilled. Served with fresh lime wedges.
Presunto
GF
Rodizio Grill's Presunto is one of our signature grilled items. A lean cut of ham that is trimmed and grilled flawlessly to perfection then basted in our signature raw sugar glaze. Presunto is best accompanied with a piece of our signature grilled glazed pineapple, but it‚Äôs also good by itself.
Lamb
*At select locations
Cordeiro
GF
This new mint lamb is marinated in garlic, white wine, mint, lemon, and a fresh herbal blend.

Fish/Seafood

Hot Side Dishes
Our freshly made Brazilian sides are included with your meal and your choices are served in abundance.
Assado

Desserts
Desserts
Enjoy a taste of Brazil's sweet side with desserts homemade daily in each of our locations. Our recipes have traveled from Brazil and are passed down from generation to generation in the family of our founder, Ivan Utrera.
Torta Brigadeiro
GF
A luxurious indulgence for chocolate lovers, it features a slice of decadent chocolate mousse torte, made with a blend of four types of chocolate. Best of all, it‚Äôs gluten-free. This delight is served a la mode with sliced bananas and fresh whipped cream.
Pudim De Leite
GF
A delicious, creamy Brazilian caramel flan ‚Äì the most incredible flan you've ever tasted! This flan is gluten-free when ordered without the crispy wafer.
Rabanada
GF

Cr√®me Br√ªl√©e

Romeu E Julieta Style Cheesecake
GF
This creamy favorite is a perfect end to a perfect meal. You can try it the way Brazilians love it ‚Äì with luscious Brazilian guava sauce ‚Äì or with a traditional raspberry sauce.
Bolo Brigadeiro
GF
A homemade chocolate cake served with an avalanche of warm brigadeiro sauce, bananas, ice cream and whipped cream. Can also be served without ice cream and whipped cream.

Our signature Caipirinha topped off with refreshing Guaran√°.

Fruit of your choice blended with ice and Brazilian cacha√ßa*. Choose from strawberry, guava, mango, pineapple, passion fruit, raspberry, coconut, and orange. *Also available with vodka. Just ask your server.

Fresh limes and mint combined with soda and rum.

GF
Passion fruit and a blend of juices served with vodka.
Rodizio Sangria
GF
A unique blend of fresh citrus juices, melon, triple sec, brandy and your choice of red or white wine, served over ice with Guaran√°.
Rodizio's Pi√±a Colada
GF
Our signature Pi√±a Colada features coconut rum and light rum blended with cream of coconut, vanilla ice cream, and fresh pineapple, topped with a dark rum float. Served in a freshly carved pineapple. Omit the rum and enjoy a non-alcoholic drink option - perfect for kids!
Other Drinks
Rodizio Limeade (Regular & Diet)
GF
Made with fresh limes and cream. It's a treat for your taste buds. You can also have your own personal touch and add any of the juices below. Try Rodizio Frozen Limeade, extremely refreshing!
Bahia Breeze
GF
Fresh cut pineapple and limes blended with a hint of mint into a refreshing "breeze" of a drink.
Guaran√° Antartica

Naturally flavored premium soda. Guaran√° is a berry grown in the Amazon region. It is also Brazil's most traditional soft drink.

Gather all of your friends and family and come experience the excitement of our famous Hibachi show! If you‚Äôre coming from I-4, take exit 74A for Sand Lake Road and go East towards International Drive. You will turn right, towards the Orlando Eye (The Giant Ferris Wheel), and it will be 1/4 of a mile down on your right hand side.

Book a date to commemorate any occasion with us: birthdays, graduations, anniversaries, corporate gatherings, and other special events! Gather your group around the grill and indulge in the pleasures of genuine Japanese cuisine, all while enjoying captivating entertainment. Take a break and experience world-class entertainment up close during lunch! Book your reservation today for an unforgettable celebration!
Due to our unique communal seating arrangement, please expect a short wait time with your reservation upon checking in with a complete party.
An automatic 18% service charge will be applied to all checks. 100% of service charge is paid out to our employees.
Private tables can be requested by smaller parties. There is a $500 spending minimum for each private table reserved.
We offer limited online booking availability, with communal seating, for large parties 11-20.
For parties 20+ or large parties requesting a booking outside of online availability, please contact your preferred Kobe location by completing our online
inquiry form
to reserve through a manager with a banquet menu. We cannot guarantee that reservations booked separately will be sat together.

Best Food
Our menu has pages of delicious food and drinks, and some of our favorites are below. From vegetarian and gluten-free options to donut holes, our menu caters to almost every taste. Treat yourself to something new or get a shareable for your whole crew. Then, top it off with one of our specialty drinks and keep on playing.
